1
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,340
=Stealing Heart=

2
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,020
=Episode 15=
(Separation)

3
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,150
Chuning.

4
00:00:51,759 --> 00:00:53,950
You've been asleep for days.

5
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,509
Wake up soon.

6
00:00:58,280 --> 00:01:00,029
Chuning.

7
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:03,270
It's alright.

8
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:06,110
If you don't wake up,

9
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:08,910
I'll come find you.

10
00:01:11,512 --> 00:01:13,150
Wake up, okay?

11
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:20,030
Siyan.

12
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:23,190
You haven't eaten or drunk for days.

13
00:01:23,599 --> 00:01:25,750
If she knew,

14
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:28,270
she would be heartbroken.

15
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:05,318
(Lu Residence)

16
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,839
Siyan, I was wrong.

17
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:09,079
I was just confused for a moment.

18
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:12,430
I did all this because I love you.

19
00:02:14,319 --> 00:02:15,470
Wretched wench.

20
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,870
How dare you harm my daughter?

21
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,989
Siyan, send her to the police.

22
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,710
Mrs. Lu.

23
00:02:23,319 --> 00:02:25,229
You're abandoning me too?

24
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,750
You really want to
send me to the police?

25
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:33,669
Please don't send me there.

26
00:02:34,759 --> 00:02:36,269
Siyan.

27
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:41,910
You tricked Lin Chuning into that car.

28
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,679
Who told you
to tamper with Lu Siyan's car?

29
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:45,910
Or she
wouldn't have gotten into the car.

30
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:47,989
We agreed to cooperate.

31
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:50,350
But if you hurt the person I love,

32
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,549
I'll return it double.

33
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:56,549
Your job
is to find Chuning's whereabouts.

34
00:02:57,120 --> 00:02:58,878
Mochen.

35
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:02,190
You'll get Chuning,
and I'll get Lu Siyan.

36
00:03:02,360 --> 00:03:04,989
After taking over
the Lu family's fortune,

37
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:08,030
we'll be the biggest winners.

38
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:11,430
(Xiaorou is already in cahoots
with Shen Mochen.)

39
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,758
(With him around,)

40
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:15,069
(Xiaorou will show up sooner or later.)

41
00:03:15,080 --> 00:03:18,150
(Then she'll hurt Chuning even more.)

42
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,870
Chuning.

43
00:03:22,879 --> 00:03:24,438
I'm begging you.

44
00:03:24,439 --> 00:03:26,318
For the sake of our sisterhood,

45
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,989
you won't abandon me.

46
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,069
Chuning.

47
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,598
I admit everything was my fault.

48
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,590
Chuning.

49
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:34,350
You're real siblings.

50
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:37,310
Help me talk to Siyan.

51
00:03:37,719 --> 00:03:39,430
Chuning.

52
00:03:41,879 --> 00:03:43,590
Have you said enough?

53
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:52,430
(If I don't play along with her,)

54
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:56,669
(this wretched wench
will expose that Siyan isn't my son.)

55
00:04:03,919 --> 00:04:04,959
Siyan.

56
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,630
Didn't I say

57
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:09,229
I'd kill you if you touched her again?

58
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:11,878
Kill me.

59
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,310
You won't dare.

60
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:16,190
You won't send me to the police either.

61
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:18,030
Once I'm out,

62
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:20,270
what will happen to Chuning?

63
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,599
Siyan.

64
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,159
It's okay if you don't love me.

65
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,150
Just let me stay by your side.

66
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:29,429
You're siblings. I'm helping you.

67
00:04:30,519 --> 00:04:32,629
Siyan.

68
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:41,229
Siyan.

69
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,950
I only want to help you.

70
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,789
Just be with me,

71
00:04:46,959 --> 00:04:49,189
and I won't touch Chuning again.

72
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:54,109
I'm happy
as long as I can stay with you.

73
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:56,438
Siyan.

74
00:04:56,439 --> 00:04:58,669
You two can never be together.

75
00:05:20,319 --> 00:05:21,390
Chuning.

76
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:25,910
Mochen.

77
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,878
Don't worry.

78
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:30,510
I'm not here to take you away.

79
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:33,150
Xiaorou told me everything.

80
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,789
You must be hurting.

81
00:05:37,839 --> 00:05:40,910
Since when are you two so close?

82
00:05:41,879 --> 00:05:43,910
We both have unreciprocated love.

83
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:46,549
I guess we sympathize with each other.

84
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,270
Chuning.

85
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,599
The best way

86
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:56,270
to forget a relationship

87
00:05:56,959 --> 00:05:58,910
is to start a new one.

88
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,030
Marry me.

89
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,030
But I don't love you.

90
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,070
That's alright.

91
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:10,549
Feelings can be developed over time.

92
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:12,799
Mochen.

93
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:16,470
I used to think love didn't matter.

94
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:19,078
Then, I met Siyan

95
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,910
and realized

96
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,270
love is the purest thing in life.

97
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:26,470
It shouldn't be tainted by impurities.

98
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,229
It's alright.

99
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:31,869
I don't mind you using me.

100
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,830
Thank you.

101
00:06:40,439 --> 00:06:41,549
Chuning.

102
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,109
We've got time ahead of us.

103
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:47,309
I'll go now.

104
00:07:07,879 --> 00:07:09,030
Chuning.

105
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:11,470
Siyan has accepted me.

106
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,070
Impossible.

107
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,910
Stop sowing discord.

108
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,390
Siyan told me

109
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,950
that you're his birth sister.

110
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,789
You two can't be together.

111
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:28,229
Chuning.

112
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:30,629
I just want to help you both.

113
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:33,789
I don't want to see you two miserable.

114
00:07:33,839 --> 00:07:34,638
So

115
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,869
I marrying Siyan is the best solution.

116
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,150
But maybe it's better this way.

117
00:07:39,639 --> 00:07:41,789
You're his sister,

118
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,679
so you're my sister too.

119
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,989
Didn't you always want that?

120
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,229
Get lost.

121
00:07:52,399 --> 00:07:54,919
I hate being called "sister".

122
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,869
Look at me now.

123
00:07:57,639 --> 00:07:59,309
Are you happy?

124
00:08:00,319 --> 00:08:01,950
Are you satisfied?

125
00:08:18,959 --> 00:08:19,989
Siyan.

126
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,510
Siyan.

127
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:27,150
I just saw Chief Shen find Chuning.

128
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:46,278
The chef here is French.

129
00:08:46,279 --> 00:08:48,158
Their steak is the most authentic.

130
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:50,509
I've long wanted to bring you here.

131
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,350
This way, sir.

132
00:09:01,534 --> 00:09:03,302
What we ordered last time was good.

133
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:04,699
We'll order this then.

134
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:06,830
Wow, what a coincidence.

135
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,430
Mind if we join you?

136
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:11,070
Please enjoy.

137
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:28,558
Chuning.

138
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:30,319
Now that I'm with Siyan,

139
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,518
I hope

140
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:33,389
you'll let go of the past.

141
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,830
Chuning can't drink much.

142
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,790
I'll drink for her.

143
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:43,710
Chief Shen and Chuning are so in love.

144
00:09:43,799 --> 00:09:46,350
We should be able
to drink at your wedding soon.

145
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,199
He's just a fiancé.

146
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:50,599
Whether it lasts

147
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,310
is unknown.

148
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:55,710
Chuning already said yes.

149
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,590
We'll be married very soon.

150
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,310
Chuning.

151
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:04,070
Congratulations.

152
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,909
I'm not worthy

153
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:07,350
of your congratulations.

154
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,550
Do you want me to congratulate you?

155
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,670
Do you want to?

156
00:10:13,879 --> 00:10:15,029
I don't want to.

157
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:17,590
Who are you to say no?

158
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,350
I'm talking to my sister.

159
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:20,629
Stay out of it.

160
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,229
It's a rare happy occasion.

161
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,350
Cheer up.

162
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:27,029
Let's eat.

163
00:10:35,679 --> 00:10:36,918
Now you understand

164
00:10:36,919 --> 00:10:37,878
why

165
00:10:37,879 --> 00:10:40,149
I couldn't wait to get rid of you

166
00:10:40,679 --> 00:10:42,319
since you entered

167
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,190
the Lu family.

168
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:46,310
I saw how Siyan looked at you

169
00:10:46,440 --> 00:10:49,550
at the birthday party.

170
00:10:49,559 --> 00:10:51,389
I feared he'd fall for you.

171
00:10:51,960 --> 00:10:54,149
I feared this would happen.

172
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,710
That's why

173
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:59,149
I could accept Xiaorou as my daughter,

174
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:02,670
but I had to destroy you.

175
00:11:04,159 --> 00:11:05,350
So,

176
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:08,590
was it because I was stillborn

177
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:11,909
or because

178
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,350
I was a girl

179
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:16,029
when you abandoned me?

180
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,839
I understand now.

181
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:27,470
Chuning, just leave.

182
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,989
You're abandoning me again?

183
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:36,918
I'm not abandoning you.

184
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,830
I'm sending you to school.

185
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:40,199
It's better

186
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,239
than you two
suffering like this all day.

187
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,839
I'm afraid you'll end up

188
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,710
making a huge mistake if this goes on.

189
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:49,389
How is that not abandonment?

190
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:52,149
Every single time,

191
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,830
you give me up first.

192
00:11:55,039 --> 00:11:56,229
Don't you?

193
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,999
She doesn't have to leave.

194
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,229
I will.

195
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,670
No.

196
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:04,359
You're the only son.

197
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,719
Your father won't agree.

198
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:07,558
I've already applied to a school

199
00:12:07,559 --> 00:12:08,989
to study business.

200
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,278
When I graduate,

201
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:12,149
I can return
to manage Lu Department Store.

202
00:12:12,720 --> 00:12:14,310
He won't say no.

203
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:30,319
Using studying as a cover,

204
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:32,629
I can focus on aviation school.

205
00:12:33,112 --> 00:12:35,470
No more hiding.

206
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,149
After I leave,

207
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,839
I hope

208
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,670
you can marry someone

209
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,389
who truly loves you.

210
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,509
I can't marry

211
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:04,029
the one I love.

212
00:13:25,159 --> 00:13:27,310
Tomorrow is my last day here.

213
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:29,430
Let's be reckless one last time.

214
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,909
Live differently.

215
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,070
Give me a bite.

216
00:13:54,919 --> 00:13:56,109
Give it back.

217
00:13:56,639 --> 00:13:59,509
No.

218
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:02,269
- It's mine now.
- Give it to me.

219
00:14:03,039 --> 00:14:04,470
Give it.

220
00:14:05,159 --> 00:14:06,550
Let me have one bite first.

221
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:20,550
I saw you.

222
00:14:21,879 --> 00:14:23,359
Did I scare you?

223
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,950
You're so childish.

224
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:25,959
Give it to me.

225
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:26,989
No.

226
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,070
No.

227
00:14:30,712 --> 00:14:31,079
What?

228
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,158
Give it to me.

229
00:14:32,159 --> 00:14:33,670
Call me "Brother" and I'll give it.

230
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,989
Hold on tight.

231
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,190
I'm speeding up.

232
00:14:41,310 --> 00:14:47,340
♪My heart stays warm,
even after the lights go out♪

233
00:14:47,870 --> 00:14:53,710
♪Holding on to our fate,
I don't feel cold♪

234
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:57,109
Is it pretty?

235
00:14:57,639 --> 00:14:59,149
Yes.

236
00:14:59,879 --> 00:15:01,070
Take it.

237
00:15:03,399 --> 00:15:05,070
It's finished.

238
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,989
This is all your fault.

239
00:15:09,879 --> 00:15:11,232
Let's go.

240
00:15:11,233 --> 00:15:12,950
I'll buy more for you.

241
00:15:13,039 --> 00:15:14,158
Really?

242
00:15:14,159 --> 00:15:15,670
Let's buy more then!

243
00:15:18,300 --> 00:15:20,239
♪With you♪

244
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:24,839
(May Lin Chuning always be joyful
and free from worries.)

245
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:32,643
♪When your presence
lit the path I longed to find♪

246
00:15:33,279 --> 00:15:37,519
(May Lu Siyan always be safe
and has everything work out for him.)

247
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:44,036
♪Wait for the dark to make peace♪

248
00:15:44,399 --> 00:15:45,909
I hope we won't be siblings again

249
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:50,550
in our next life.

250
00:15:51,440 --> 00:15:52,389
No.

251
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,989
I hope we never meet again

252
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:59,749
in our next life.

253
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,590
As the saying goes,

254
00:16:13,679 --> 00:16:15,398
a mother worries
when her child travels far.

255
00:16:15,399 --> 00:16:18,229
Not to mention,
you're going all the way to Hong Kong.

256
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:20,269
If you crave something, just buy it.

257
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,590
If you need anything, write home.

258
00:16:24,639 --> 00:16:26,909
Don't let yourself suffer.

259
00:16:27,279 --> 00:16:28,389
I got it.

260
00:16:30,080 --> 00:16:31,749
I'll take good care of myself.

261
00:16:31,879 --> 00:16:33,029
Study hard.

262
00:16:33,639 --> 00:16:34,790
Make us proud.

263
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:38,950
Don't bring your bad habits with you.

264
00:16:39,639 --> 00:16:40,989
Got it.

265
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:50,839
Lu Department Stores is busy.

266
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,199
Your sister couldn't get away.

267
00:16:52,200 --> 00:16:53,710
She won't be seeing you off.

268
00:16:55,840 --> 00:16:57,439
Think of me now and then,

269
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:59,269
but don't miss me too much.

270
00:16:59,399 --> 00:17:01,350
Live your life well.

271
00:17:02,519 --> 00:17:04,109
I'm off.

272
00:17:16,886 --> 00:17:18,816
♪Can I take♪

273
00:17:19,526 --> 00:17:22,736
♪The whispers in my ear seriously?♪

274
00:17:23,686 --> 00:17:25,119
Come back soon.

275
00:17:25,120 --> 00:17:26,776
♪You didn't ask♪

276
00:17:27,653 --> 00:17:32,503
♪And I pretended not to see or hear it♪

277
00:17:32,786 --> 00:17:36,483
♪I feel heartbroken, but I bear it♪

278
00:17:36,973 --> 00:17:40,249
♪I waited and waited♪

279
00:17:40,250 --> 00:17:44,852
♪Even if I disguise all my past♪

280
00:17:44,853 --> 00:17:49,169
♪I just can't hide my feelings for you♪

281
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:52,325
♪The more I panic, the deeper it burns♪

282
00:17:52,326 --> 00:17:54,039
♪Push you away, then pull you close♪

283
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,559
♪The more I try to run away,
the more I yearn for it♪

284
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:59,379
♪Thought we'd walk through
a world of wonder♪

285
00:17:59,380 --> 00:18:01,219
♪Savor it, slow and sweet♪

286
00:18:01,220 --> 00:18:05,519
♪But in the end, it all shattered on me♪

287
