310
00:19:07,480 --> 00:19:10,149
(But I can't help myself.)

311
00:19:10,706 --> 00:19:14,139
♪You're the only one I can't fathom♪

312
00:19:14,140 --> 00:19:18,339
♪But at the end of twilight♪

313
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:20,919
