323
00:20:02,110 --> 00:20:05,869
♪Who would look back from so far away?♪

324
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:09,009
♪All you can see is frosty smoke♪

325
00:20:09,010 --> 00:20:12,469
♪Time rushes by, turning hair white♪

326
00:20:12,470 --> 00:20:15,809
♪Shattered memories
still linger in my heart♪

327
00:20:15,810 --> 00:20:19,549
♪Who embraces the moonlight
from so far away?♪

328
00:20:19,550 --> 00:20:24,190
♪Like a fleeting dream from that year♪

329
00:20:45,279 --> 00:20:46,270
Miss.

330
